stony /ˈstəʊnɪ/

(stonier,stoniest) 

1. ADJ Stony ground is rough and contains a lot of stones. 多石的 

例： The steep, stony ground is well drained. 多石陡峭的地面很容易排水。 

2. ADJ A stony expression or attitude does not show any sympathy or friendliness. 冷漠的 

例： She gave me the stoniest look I ever got. 她向我投以我所见过的最冷漠的眼神。

